This is a delivery image, please perform final installation steps befor usage.

1. Change Host name
       'vcXX' - XX being preferred board number; it is used to derive MAC and IP addresses
  echo 'vcXX' > /etc/hostname

2. Replace this startup message by either
  echo 'RSwitch1 image -- VC2 mainboard' > /etc/motd
  echo 'RSwitch1 image -- VC3 mainboard' > /etc/motd

3. Restart the box
  sync
  init 6

